    {
      "id": "PopularPost234696",
      "post_content": "@Necrolysis It's not right to say its better, the two do different things. [Desecrated Earth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Desecrated Earth) will get you card advantage, which is nice, but this can be dropped first turn for discard. Remember, you CANNOT cast both halves of a double card at once.  \n  \nPeople who keep pointing out that there are better cards for either half are missing the point; being able to do either from one card is the advantage. Neither half on it's own should be a top tier card.  \n  \nI would say this is a mediocre card only because discard and land destruction aren't things every deck needs. truthfully I don't think I have seen a deck that does a lot of both. If your deck DOES do both, then this is a great addition I suppose.",
      "posted_by": "Enelysios",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost234696\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">@Necrolysis It's not right to say its better, the two do different things. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Desecrated Earth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Desecrated Earth\">Desecrated Earth</a> will get you card advantage, which is nice, but this can be dropped first turn for discard. Remember, you CANNOT cast both halves of a double card at once.<br/><br/>People who keep pointing out that there are better cards for either half are missing the point; being able to do either from one card is the advantage. Neither half on it's own should be a top tier card.<br/><br/>I would say this is a mediocre card only because discard and land destruction aren't things every deck needs. truthfully I don't think I have seen a deck that does a lot of both. If your deck DOES do both, then this is a great addition I suppose.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '234696'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80532\">Enelysios</span>\r\n                                (3/25/2012 11:40:18 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n  